oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Biff Collie Steel Guitar Samples - Tape 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording is of a number of samples featuring a steel guitar. The recordings are performed by an unidentified performer for Biff Collie's Happy Hour. Tape is labeled as tape 1. The recording is from an unknown date.
